<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤٦٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5178">قَبِيصَةُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">إِبْرَاهِيمَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/710">الْأَسْوَدِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«تُوُفِّيَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> وَدِرْعُهُ مَرْهُونَةٌ عِنْدَ يَهُودِيٍّ بِثَلَاثِينَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>